{"product_id":"madara-the-brow-pencil-medium-brown-1g-copy","title":"MÁDARA The Brow Pencil Dark Brown 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis creamy eyebrow pencil glides onto the skin smoothly, shaping your brows for a defined and polished look. Formulated with mineral pigments, providing long-lasting shades that blend seamlessly with the colour of your natural brow hairs. Ideal for drawing precise, hair-like strokes or for completely filling in your brows. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Brow Pencil features a wooden barrel and recyclable plastic caps while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eComb and shape your eyebrows with the built-in spoolie, following their natural curve. Create a natural brow look by drawing soft, hair-like strokes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eC10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e17% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\